  "$id": "https://taxat.dev/schemas/twin_delta_arc.schema.json",
  "title": "TwinDeltaArc",
  "description": "Cross-source delta-bridge contract for Twin Lens rendering. This schema freezes the normalized comparison key, the comparison_key_ingredients that feed that key, subject being compared, terminal delta class, materiality, resolution posture, priority rank, basis posture, and any blocking or limitation rationale attached to the bridge.",
